衰過大陸啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家一樣有人北上搵老婆<br />\n只不過小過以前啫<br />\n而且要搵點會搵唔到啊 唔好戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係個句 睇你咩質素就揀翻咩質素啦"}]}